<i>He's L?</i>

19
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:46,190
<i>He's different
from what I imagined...</i>

20
00:01:50,403 --> 00:01:51,946
I am Detective Superintendent Yagami
of the National Police Agency.

21
00:01:52,655 --> 00:01:53,656
Uh, I'm Matsuda.

22
00:01:53,906 --> 00:01:54,949
I'm Aizawa.

23
00:01:54,991 --> 00:01:56,659
- I'm Mogi.
- I'm Ukita.

24
00:01:58,578 --> 00:01:59,621
I'm sorry we're late.

25
00:02:00,288 --> 00:02:01,623
These five are our current...

26
00:02:01,831 --> 00:02:02,832
Bang!

27
00:02:03,499 --> 00:02:04,125
What...?

28
00:02:04,250 --> 00:02:05,209
Is this some kind of joke?

29
